trans-unit.source: Represents a read-only collection of <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.ManifestSignatureInformation"></xref> objects.
To get a ManifestSignatureInformationCollection collection, call one of the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.ManifestSignatureInformation.VerifySignature%2A> method overloads.
trans-unit.target: ManifestSignatureInformationCollection 컬렉션을 가져오려면 호출 중 하나는 <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.ManifestSignatureInformation.VerifySignature%2A>메서드 오버 로드.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.ManifestSignatureInformation.VerifySignature%2A>

trans-unit.source: Each collection contains a <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.ManifestSignatureInformation> object for each manifest that was verified by the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.ManifestSignatureInformation.VerifySignature%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 각 컬렉션에 포함 된 <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.ManifestSignatureInformation>확인 된 각 매니페스트에 대 한 개체는 <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.ManifestSignatureInformation.VerifySignature%2A>메서드.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.ManifestSignatureInformation.VerifySignature%2A> </xref:System.Security.Cryptography.ManifestSignatureInformation>
